With the advancements in Artificial Intelligence (AI) technologies, Google has been integrating AI capabilities into its Workspace suite to make it more efficient and user-friendly and more suitable for hybrid work life

Google Workspace uses AI-powered grammar suggestions in Google Docs, Google Sheets, and Google Slides

Voice typing is another AI capability offered by Google Workspace. The system allows users to dictate text using their voice in Google Docs.

Portrait restore uses Google AI to enhance video quality in Google Meet, even if youâ€™re in a dimly lit room or have poor WiFi connection.

Google's Smart Reply is an AI-powered feature that suggests responses to emails in Gmail.

The Explore feature is an AI-powered tool that helps users find information and insights in Google Sheets, Google Docs, and Google Slides.

Google Meet now has an AI-powered live transcription feature that transcribes the audio in real-time.
